title: FRIDAY - Playoff positioning on the line in Week 17 2021
itunes:title: FRIDAY - Playoff positioning on the line in Week 17 2021
description:
The Dolphins suffering a big loss at the QB position (0:11) ahead of their game against the Bills. The Browns hit with more COVID-19 issues (0:46) and the Packers get some bad news about one of their star players (1:54). On the flip side, Washington gets an encouraging update on Alex Smith's injury (2:21) and Cowboys head coach Mike McCarthy (3:34) happy to be playing meaningful football in December
